# ─── Merge strategy overrides ────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# INNOVATION_LOG.md is an append-only log written by autonomous auto-innovation
# branches.  Multiple branches can land concurrently and both write to this
# file, producing repeated merge conflicts.
# The `union` driver resolves conflicts by keeping all unique lines from both
# sides — exactly the right behaviour for an append-only log file.
# This means git NEVER produces a conflict marker for this file again.
INNOVATION_LOG.md merge=union

# Same strategy for any individual innovation proposal files that may accumulate
# in the innovations/ directory.
innovations/*.md merge=union
